---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Teaching notes, pedagogy reflections, and research-in-progress from Dr. Hadiza Galadima. Biostatistics, public health, and applied statistical reasoning.
permalink: /blog/
schemaType: CollectionPage
---

<article class="post-index">
  <header class="post-index-header">
    <h1 class="post-index-title">Blog</h1>
    <p class="post-index-kicker">Teaching notes, pedagogy reflections, and research-in-progress. Written for fellow educators and my own students.</p>
  </header>

  <ul class="post-index-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
      <li class="post-index-item">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-index-link">
          <time class="post-index-date" datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
          <h2 class="post-index-item-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.summary %}<p class="post-index-summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          {% if post.data.tags and post.data.tags.length %}
            <p class="post-index-tags">{% for tag in post.data.tags %}<span class="post-tag">#{{ tag }}</span> {% endfor %}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      </li>
    {% else %}
      <li class="post-index-empty">No posts yet. Check back soon.</li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</article>
